<br>
Oh crap the Pally is attacking me, and not my Hero buddy, I better really concentrate on dodging/parrying:<br>
<br>
Defense -*-------- Offense<br>
<br>
Okay good, he's back to the Hero now, I can wail away on him again:<br>
Defense ---------* Offense<br>
<br>
